headline: If I Could Only Buy and Hold a Single Stock, This Would Be It
summary: Personally, my favorite stock, the single one that I would hold if I couldn't own any others, is Costco (NASDAQ: COST).  This retailer's simple business remains poised to continue generating handsome profit growth for the foreseeable future.  For those unfamiliar with it, Costco charges an annual fee to shop at its warehouses.
